name: Animal Safari Jeep Parking
description:
Go for a wild ride on a safari with animals and things to see!

Park your jeep and other vehicles and take care of the wilderness! Those animals need feeding! Who is going to look after them? Become a real park ranger!

- 3D graphics and touch gameplay!
- Lots of varieties of animals!
- Multiple missions like parking and racing!

DOWNLOAD AND DRIVE TODAY!
